350" />The community is welcome to use the facilities at BYU-Idaho within the authorized limitations.</p>
<p>Here are answers to some <a href="x41318.xml">frequently asked questions</a> from other community users about making reservations at BYU-Idaho.</p>
<p>You may contact our Scheduling Office during normal business hours (except Tuesday when we closed for devotionals from 2-3 p.m.).</p>
<p>Getting started can be as simple as 1-2-3.</p>
<p>1. Please take a few minutes to become familiar with our <a href="x41328.xml">policies</a>.</p>
<p>2. Think through what you want your event to be. Use our <a href="x42172.xml">event planning</a> tips to understand which part is yours and which part is ours. You can even <a href="http://scheduling.byui.edu">browse</a> to see what spaces may be open on the date and time you need.</p>
<p>3. Contact us for pricing and to submit your request. For mutual convenience, use the online <a href="Documents/scheduling-office/Off_Campus_Form_distributed.pdf">Non-University Organization Scheduling Request form</a> to submit your needs up to 90 days prior to the event. Be sure to save a copy of the completed form before submitting it as an email attachment to <a href="mailto:scheduling@byui.edu">scheduling@byui.edu</a></p>]]></BodyCopy><xPower Type="GroupStart" Name="PageComponents" label="Page Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" GroupStart=""><xPower Type="List" Name="OptionalColumnComponent" label="Optional Column Components" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="" List=""><xpowercomponent_Optional Type="Component" Component="" Name="Optional" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" CompTypes="FacebookComponent;Image;ColumnTextComponent;Media;Quote" Expanded="false" /></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn1" label="QuickLinks Column 1" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn2" label="QuickLinks Column 2" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="Component" Name="QuickLinksColumn3" label="QuickLinks Column 3" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="QuickLinksComponent" /></xPower><xPower Type="Component" Name="HighlightedLinks" label="Highlighted Links" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="x42569" CompTypes="HighlightedLinksComponent" /><xPower Type="List" Name="ContentSnippet" label="Content Snippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="false"><xPower Type="Component" Name="ContentSnippet" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Component="" CompTypes="ContentSnippet" /></xPower><xPower Type="Navigation" Name="AncestorN